column4: El Gigante, Sting, and The Steiner Brothers (Rick Steiner and Scott Steiner) defeated Abdullah the Butcher, The Diamond Studd, Cactus Jack and Big Van Vader
Big Josh and P.N. News defeated The Creatures (Creature 1 and Creature 2)
Johnny B. Badd defeated Jimmy Garvin
Steve Austin (c) wrestled Dustin Rhodes to a time-limit draw
The Halloween Phantom defeated Tom Zenk
The Enforcers (c) (Arn Anderson and Larry Zbyszko) defeated The Patriots (Todd Champion and Firebreaker Chip)
Lex Luger (c) (with Harley Race) defeated Ron Simmons (with Dusty Rhodes)
